tldr: The user requested a comprehensive aesthetic review and improvement for
  their sleep questionnaire app. The agent implemented a new sleep-themed color
  palette, redesigned the form layout and UI components, and ensured consistent
  styling across all sections. Additionally, a console error related to null
  input values was identified and fixed, and further aesthetic refinements were
  made based on user feedback.
overview: The user initiated a request for a complete aesthetic overhaul of
  their sleep questionnaire application, feeling its current design was too
  generic. The agent began by conducting a thorough review of the existing
  styling, identifying areas for improvement in color palette, typography,
  spacing, form elements, and overall visual interest. A new sleep-themed color
  palette was introduced, along with custom utility classes for gradients and
  shadows. The main questionnaire form layout was redesigned with decorative
  background elements, an improved progress indicator, and a subtle star pattern
  overlay on card headers. All core UI components like checkboxes, radio
  buttons, sliders, and progress bars were enhanced with better visual feedback
  and transitions. The introduction and all subsequent questionnaire sections
  were updated to reflect the new cohesive styling, replacing generic gray boxes
  with themed card-like groupings. During the review, a console error related to
   values being passed to input components was identified and fixed by
  modifying the  component to safely handle  values. Following
  initial implementation, the user provided feedback on remaining aesthetic
  inconsistencies in the report section, specifically regarding hardcoded card
  header gradients and alert colors. The agent then addressed these by updating
  all report card headers to use the consistent sleep-themed gradient and
  replacing hardcoded alert colors with newly defined theme-based utility
  classes, along with increasing the opacity of section borders for better
  definition. The outcome is a visually cohesive, calming, and professional
  sleep questionnaire application.
